str2: To cause to drink, give to drink; irrigate, water. From a derivative of the alternate of pino; to furnish drink, irrigate.
No, not. Also ouk, and ouch a primary word; the absolute negative adverb; no or not.
Food of any kind. From the base of bibrosko; food, especially articles allowed or forbidden by the Jewish law.
For. A primary particle; properly, assigning a reason.

word: you were not yet ready [for solid food].

str2: (a) I am powerful, have (the) power, (b) I am able, I can. Of uncertain affinity; to be able or possible.
But, except, however. Neuter plural of allos; properly, other things, i.e. contrariwise.
